---
// Hero estático para LCP otimizado
---

<section class="w-full overflow-hidden hero-section">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 relative">

    <!-- Right Image -->
    <div class="absolute right-0 md:right-4 lg:right-12 bottom-0 pointer-events-none hero-image hidden sm:block">
      <img
        src="/patient1.webp"
        alt="Paciente transformada após tratamento com cannabis medicinal"
        fetchpriority="high"
        decoding="sync"
        loading="eager"
        width="512"
        height="512"
        class="h-[320px] md:h-[420px] lg:h-[520px] w-auto object-cover object-top rounded-tl-[3rem]"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Left Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-28 md:max-w-[52%] lg:max-w-[58%]">

      <!-- Social Proof Badge -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-8 hero-badge">
        <img
          src="/googleavaliacoes.png"
          alt="Google 5 estrelas"
          class="h-5 w-auto"
          loading="eager"
          width="100"
          height="20"
        />
        <span class="text-white/90 text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap" style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;">
          +3.000 pacientes atendidos
        </span>
      </div>

      <!-- H1 -->
      <h1
        class="text-[1.9rem] md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.25rem] text-white mb-5 leading-[1.15] font-extrabold hero-title"
        style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;"
      >
        <span class="block md:hidden">Você não precisa<br/>viver com dor,<br/>insônia ou ansiedade.</span>
        <span class="hidden md:block">Você não precisa viver<br/>com dor, insônia<br/>ou ansiedade.</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p
        class="text-base md:text-lg text-white/80 mb-8 max-w-sm md:max-w-md leading-relaxed hero-subtitle"
        style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;"
      >
        Avaliação médica online com especialista em cannabis medicinal, sem sair de casa, sem fila, a partir de R$50.
      </p>

      <!-- CTAs -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-3 hero-cta-wrapper">
        <button
          type="button"
          class="open-chat inline-flex items-center justify-center px-7 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:opacity-90 transition-all duration-200 cta-primary"
          style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;"
          data-cta="hero_primary"
        >
          Quero minha avaliação por R$50
        </button>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="open-chat inline-flex items-center justify-center px-7 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white rounded-full border border-white/40 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-200"
          style="font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;"
          data-cta="hero_receita"
        >
          Já tenho receita →
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    background-color: #2D1B69;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    background-color: #00B383;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 179, 131, 0.35);
  }
  .cta-primary:hover {
    background-color: #009e74;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .hero-image {
      animation: slideInRight 0.8s ease-out 0.1s both;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      animation: fadeInDown 0.5s ease-out 0.1s both;
    }
    .hero-title {
      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.15s both;
    }
    .hero-subtitle {
      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both;
    }
    .hero-cta-wrapper {
      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.25s both;
    }
  }

  @keyframes slideInRight {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(80px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeInDown {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-16px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.hero-cta-wrapper [data-cta]').forEach(link => {
    link.addEventListener('click', () => {
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      window.dataLayer.push({
        event: 'cta_click',
        cta_location: link.getAttribute('data-cta'),
      });
    });
  });
</script>
